      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·齊風·011.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">猗嗟.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>猗嗟昌兮！頎而長兮。抑若揚兮，美目揚兮。巧趨蹌兮。射則臧兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Alas for him, so handsome and accomplished !
How grandly tall !
With what elegance in his high forehead !
With what motion of his beautiful eyes !
With what skill in the swift movements of his feet !
With what mastery of archery !</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-qifeng-011__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
