      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">stanza</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·齊風·011.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">猗嗟.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>猗嗟名兮！美目清兮。儀既成兮，終日射侯，不出正兮，展我甥兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Alas for him, so famous !
His beautiful eyes how clear !
His manners how complete !
Shooting all day at the target,
And never lodging outside the bird-square !
Indeed our rulers nephew !</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
